    <div class = "information">
      <h1> History </h1>
      <p>France is an independent nation in Western Europe and the center of a large overseas administration. It is the third-largest European nation. France is known for having primarily french speaking citizens. At once universal and particular, French culture has spread far and greatly influenced the development of art and science. The capital and by far the most important city of France is Paris, home to the Eiffel Tower.
      </p>
    </div>
